ia.org/resource/WFLA-TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Originally appeared onE!\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Online  Eva Mendesis giving the2024 Olympicsa perfect 10.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream Connecticut News for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut\", \"score\": 0.9657476956431588, \"rank\": 0.033797098043096205, \"text\": \"Connecticut\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connecticut\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Hitch\\\" star and her longtime loveRyan Goslingwere seen cheering on the athletes at the women's gymnastics uneven bars final in Paris Aug. 4.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999990222932, \"rank\": 9.77738305755271e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while they were joined by daughters Esmeralda, 9, and Amada, 8, Mendes is very grateful her girls were not part of the spotlight.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_corvette_Esmeralda\", \"score\": 0.9746585340152729, \"rank\": 0.024972323385895723, \"text\": \"Esmeralda\", \"types\": [\"Q11446\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_corvette_Esmeralda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chilean_corvette_Esmeralda\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amada\", \"score\": 0.9999999872975424, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amada\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love @nbcolympics did not cut away to the kids !,\\\" Mendes wrote in anInstagram comment to a fan Aug. 6.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And most sites blurred their faces so mama bear is happy about that.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyway it felt so good to be there and feel unified with people.\\\"\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also replied to another commenter, adding, \\\"they were great about not posing the kids so l'm a grateful mama bear.\\\"\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mendes, 50, and Gosling, 43, have kept both their relationship and their family lifelargely out of the public eyesince they met on the set of 2012's \\\"The Place Beyond the Pines.\\\"\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was during the making of that film that Gosling realized just how hard he'd fallen for Mendes.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't thinking about kids before I met her, but after I met Eva, I realized that I just did not want to have kids without her,\\\" the \\\"Fall Guy\\\" actor toldGQin 2023.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And there were moments on 'The Place Beyond the Pines' where we were pretending to be a family, and I did not really want it to be pretend anymore.\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I realized that this would be a life I would be really lucky to have.\\\"\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, Gosling's family lifehas dictated many of his film choices over the years, especially his decision to take on the role of Ken in last year's hit movie, \\\"Barbie.\\\"\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1796, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1197887419226865e-13, \"text\": \"Barbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was their interest in 'Barbie,' and their disinterest in Ken that sort of started all this,\\\"he explained on \\\"The Tonight Show\\\" in April.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1197887419226865e-13, \"text\": \"Barbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's really been a team effort.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And they were on the film and they came to set when I filmed the number.\\\"\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"number\\\" of course refers tothe instantly iconic song, \\\"I am Just Ken.\\\"\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They know all the choreography better than I do\\\" he joked.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are backstage showing me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": []}]}"